</EQUATION><CHAR><LINEBREAK /></CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="87" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="22096224" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="278459"><SIZE Height="1313" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="15649" WidthRelTo="Absolute" /><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para" /><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0" /><SHAPECOMMENT>전재윤</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>= rm P it (A) rm P it (B`|`A)+ rm P it (A ^{C }` ) rm P it (B`|`A ^{C} `)</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR><LINEBREAK /></CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="24880810" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="278459"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="13017" WidthRelTo="Absolute" /><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para" /><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0" /><SHAPECOMMENT>전재윤</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT> =0.6 times 0.6+0.4 times 0.5=0.56</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR><TAB /></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>따라서 구하는 확률은</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><EQUATION BaseLine="65" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="8714779" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="296509"><SIZE Height="2580" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="15677" WidthRelTo="Absolute" /><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para" /><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0" /><SHAPECOMMENT>전재윤</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{ rm P it }(A`|`B)= it {{ rm P it }(A cap B)} over {{ rm P it }(B)} = it {0.36} over {0.56} = {9} over {14}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR /></TEXT></P></PARALIST></ENDNOTE></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>세원이가 인터넷으로 어느 맛집에 대한 후기를 검색하면 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="8714779" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="296509"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2087" WidthRelTo="Absolute" /><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para" /><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0" /><SHAPECOMMENT>전재윤</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>60`%</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>는 여자가 작성한 후기라고 한다. 이때 여자가 후기를 작성하였을 때 단어 ‘제공’이 포함될 확률은 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="24880810" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="278459"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1350" WidthRelTo="Absolute" /><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para" /><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0" /><SHAPECOMMENT>전재윤</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>0.6</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>이고, 남자가 후기를 작성하였을 때 ‘제공’이 포함될 확률은 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="22096224" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="278459"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1350" WidthRelTo="Absolute" /><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para" /><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0" /><SHAPECOMMENT>전재윤</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>0.5</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>라고 한다. 세원이가 ‘제공’이 포함된 후기를 찾았을 때, 이 후기가 여자가 작성한 후기일 확률을 구하시오.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0" ColumnBreak="true" PageBreak="false"><TEXT CharShape="0"><TABLE BorderFill="1" CellSpacing="0" ColCount="3" PageBreak="Cell" RepeatHeader="true" RowCount="2"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="24158811" Lock="false" NumberingType="Table" ZOrder="538868"><SIZE Height="2282" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="29624" WidthRelTo="Absolute" /><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para" /><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="0" Right="0" Top="0" /></SHAPEOBJECT><INSIDEMARGIN Bottom="566" Left="0" Right="0" Top="566" /><ROW><CELL BorderFill="1" ColAddr="0" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="282" Protect="false" RowAddr="0" RowSpan="1" Width="4152"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141" /><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="5"><CHAR>[출처]</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="1" ColAddr="1" ColSpan="2" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="282" Protect="false" RowAddr="0" RowSpan="1" Width="25472"> <CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141" /><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Cent