CRIPT>{ rm P it }(A)= it 0.001</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="8714779" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="296509"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6350" WidthRelTo="Absolute" /><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para" /><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0" /><SHAPECOMMENT>전재윤</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{ rm P it }(B``|`A)= it 0.9 </SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="87" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="9256272" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="314559"><SIZE Height="1313" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6771" WidthRelTo="Absolute" /><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para" /><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0" /><SHAPECOMMENT>전재윤</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{ rm P it }(B`|`A ^{C} )= it 0.1</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR /></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>검사 결과가 독감인 환자일 확률은</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="24158811" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="538868"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2175" WidthRelTo="Absolute" /><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para" /><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0" /><SHAPECOMMENT>전재윤</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{ rm P it } left ( B right )</SCRIPT></EQUATION><EQUATION BaseLine="87" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="16527048" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="278459"><SIZE Height="1313" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="10825" WidthRelTo="Absolute" /><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para" /><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0" /><SHAPECOMMENT>전재윤</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT> = it { rm P it } left (A cap B right )+ { rm P it } left (A ^{C } cap B right ) </SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR><LINEBREAK /></CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="87" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="9256272" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="314559"><SIZE Height="1313" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="15050" WidthRelTo="Absolute" /><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para" /><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0" /><SHAPECOMMENT>전재윤</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>
 ={ rm P}  LEFT (A RIGHT ) { rm P} LEFT  (B`|`A RIGHT )+ {rm P}  LEFT (A  ^{C}` RIGHT ){ rm P} LEFT  (B`|A  ^{C}`RIGHT  ) </SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR><LINEBREAK /></CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="8714779" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="296509"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="16829" WidthRelTo="Absolute" /><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para" /><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0" /><SHAPECOMMENT>전재윤</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>
 =`0.001 TIMES 0.9+0.999 TIMES 0.31=0.1008</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR /></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>따라서 구하는 확률은 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="65" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="8534273" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="574968"><SIZE Height="2580" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="17252" WidthRelTo="Absolute" /><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para" /><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0" /><SHAPECOMMENT>전재윤</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{ rm P it }(A`|`B)= it {{ rm P it }(A cap B)} over {{ rm P it }(B)} = it {0.0009} over {0.1008} = {1} over {112}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR /></TEXT></P></PARALIST></ENDNOTE></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>어느 병원에 독감 증상으로 찾아오는 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="8714779" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="296509"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2100" WidthRelTo="Absolute" /><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para" /><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0" /><SHAPECOMMENT>전재윤</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>1000</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>명의 환자 중에서 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="16527048" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="278459"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="525" WidthRelTo="Absolute" /><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para" /><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0" /><SHAPECOMMENT>전재윤</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>1</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>명이 실제로 독감 환자이고, 이 병원에서 독감 감염 여부를 판정하는 검사의 정확도는 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="22096224" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="278459"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2087" WidthRelTo="Absolute" /><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para" /><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0" /><SHAPECOMMENT>전재윤</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>90`%</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>라고 한다. 독감 증상으로 이 병원에 찾아온 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="24158811" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="538868"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2100" WidthRelTo="Absolute" /><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para" /><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0" /><SHAPECOMMENT>전재윤</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>1000</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>명의 환자의 감염 여부를 판정할 때, 검사 결과가 독감인 환자가 실제로 독감 환자일 확률을 구하시오. </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0" ColumnBreak="true" PageBreak="false"><TEXT CharShape="0"><TABLE BorderFill="1" CellSpacing="0" ColCount="3" PageBreak="Cell" RepeatHeader="true" RowCount="2"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="11679865" Lock="false" NumberingType="Table" ZOrder="296509"><SIZE Heig